rs in Vietnam</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2005</strong></td>\n			<td>- Set up standard ISO: 9001 – 2000</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2006</strong></td>\n			<td>- Professionalize internation logistic</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2007</strong></td>\n			<td>- Supply chain management</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2008</strong></td>\n			<td>- Hoang Ha International Logistic J.S.C</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2009</strong></td>\n			<td>- Has been the winner of Vietnam Excellent Brand</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2011</strong></td>\n			<td>- Established Can Tho Office</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 65),
(29, '<p>We aim to be known as professional, efficient, reliable and friendly company to deal with.</p>\n\n<p>We care about and highly value all our customer, no matter how different their requirements, products and expectations are. They all are our special clients each requiring an individual approach.</p>\n\n<p>Our experienced staff are highly trained to help the customers to overcome all and every barrier, efficiently ensuring the prompt freight forwarding and timely cargo delivery services.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 66),
(30, '<p>Refrigerated bag is GEL products are manufactured according to its advanced technology NORTHWEST USA. GEL when dissolved in a mixture of water with natural viscosity adhesive. After the freezing cold GEL always shine in temperate conditions, keep the goods always lush.</p>\n\n<p>Cold packs are not toxic and cause side effects for users.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Application:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Especially for fresh seafood and fresh vegetables for export.</li>\n	<li>Preservation of medicines.</li>\n	<li>Also GEL has other uses such as hot and cold compresses when a high fever, keep food cold for outdoor trips...</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Bags GEL liquid before using the bag in the freezer to freeze, after the bag has been frozen for the foam barrels or refrigeration equipment for storage.</li>\n	<li>GEL bags once frozen goods can be kept cold for 20 hours to melt.</li>\n	<li>Refrigerated bag can be used several times, but kept cool time will be reduced.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;<em>Should be refrigerated bags intact, no tearing the packaging, does not allow the liquid to spill out into the food and drinks.</em></p>\n\n<p><em>No food or drink - Keep out of reach of children.</em></p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><img alt="GEL - ICE PACK" src="http://www.hoangha.com/public/images/1456990227.jpg" style="width: 334px; height: 500px;" /></em></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 67),
(31, '<h2>The safest way to ship perishable items, such as food, is by packing them in dry ice.</h2>\n\n<p>Dry ice is a solid form of carbon dioxide. It does not melt like frozen water, instead it sublimates-returns to its gaseous state.</p>\n\n<p>There is no water accumulation to damage your shipment when you use dry ice.</p>\n\n<p>Federal rules that govern all shipments containing dry ice require that you place special hazardous materials labeling on your package.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="CO2 - ICE PACK" src="http://hoangha.com/images/stories/tintuc/31-07-2012/00367543.jpg" style="width: 334px; height: 500px;" /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 68),
